---
title: Roast Duck & Peppercorn Gravy with Thyme-Roasted Potatoes & Sautéed Hazelnut Veggies
description: Pep up your roast duck with a peppercorn gravy and a side of thyme roasted potatoes. What roast duck dish is complete without some veggies, especially when there are hazelnuts scattered throughout. It’s a duck feast everyone is going to love.
